modules.name: AWS.TranscribeService
modules.comments: Operations and objects for transcribing speech to text.

declarations.comments: Returns information about a transcription job. To see the status of the job, check the Status field. If the status is COMPLETE, the job is finished and you can find the results at the location specified in the TranscriptionFileUri field.
declarations.title: getTranscriptionJob

declarations.comments: Lists transcription jobs with the specified status.
declarations.title: listTranscriptionJobs

declarations.comments: Starts an asynchronous job to transcribe speech to text.
declarations.title: startTranscriptionJob

declarations.comments: There is a problem with one of the input fields. Check the S3 bucket name, make sure that the job name is not a duplicate, and confirm that you are using the correct file format. Then resend your request.
declarations.title: BadRequestException

declarations.comments: The JobName field is a duplicate of a previously entered job name. Resend your request with a different name.
declarations.title: ConflictException

declarations.comments: There was an internal error. Check the error message and try your request again.
declarations.title: InternalFailureException

declarations.comments: Either you have sent too many requests or your input file is longer than 2 hours. Wait before you resend your request, or use a smaller file and resend the request.
declarations.title: LimitExceededException

declarations.comments: Describes the input media file in a transcription request.
declarations.title: Media

declarations.comments: We can't find the requested job. Check the job name and try your request again.
declarations.title: NotFoundException

declarations.comments: Describes the output of a transcription job.
declarations.title: Transcript

declarations.comments: Describes an asynchronous transcription job that was created with the StartTranscriptionJob operation.
declarations.title: TranscriptionJob

declarations.comments: Provides a summary of information about a transcription job.
declarations.title: TranscriptionJobSummary
